    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable, budget-friendly option. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches on the side panels and some thinning paint on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car is reliable and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention or small repairs in the near future. It\u2019s a functional daily driver that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
